Package com.cinchapi.concourse.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Queryable
    Specifies the possible query operations that can occur in a column.
    Retrievable
    Specifies the possible ways in which data can be retrieved from a row and/or column.
    Revisable
    Specifies the possible revisions that can occur regarding a value in a cell located at the intersection of row and column.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractConcourseService
    Unifies all of the services defined in the Concourse API and provides some base functionality.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Queryable.SelectOperator
    The operators that can be used with Queryable.select(String, SelectOperator, Object...).
